2002-04-10 00:19  ddurham

	* src/: backend/ASoundFileManager.cpp, backend/ASoundFileManager.h,
	  backend/COSSSoundPlayer.cpp, backend/Makefile.am,
	  frontend_fox/CActionButton.cpp,
	  frontend_fox/CActionParamDialog.cpp,
